      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented V&V test suite with regression testing, version control, and independent code review consistent with MRL 5 requirements.",
      "rationale": "Solver version control and regression testing are partially documented. Independent code review has not been performed. Achieved level 2 is insufficient for MRL 5 requirement of level 4."
