      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation or equivalent GCI analysis must be performed on at least three systematically refined meshes for all five COU operating points.",
      "rationale": "GCI analysis was completed for one operating point only (2500 RPM, 4 L/min). Remaining four operating points lack discretization error estimates. Achieved level 2 is below required level 4."
