    "rationale": "The UnitOfAssurance package is accepted for submission to the regulatory dossier as a complete credibility evidence record under the Minimal profile. Note that the underlying credibility assessment outcome for the COU is Not Accepted — seven of thirteen factors were assessed with achieved levels below required levels, and six factors remain as epistemic gaps at MRL 5. The package documents all identified gaps and is accepted as a complete and honest representation of the current model credibility state for Class III VAD hemolysis prediction.",
